Finance & Accounting Assistant Job (Online E-commerce),
Jakarta, Indonesia
Country:
Indonesia
Function:
Accounting & Finance
Industry:
I.T.
Position type:
Permanent
Salary:
Negotiable
Created:
06 May 2014
Monroe Consulting Group is recruiting on behalf of an established local online E-commerce provider. Our client offers online e-commerce and search engine for buying and selling product. Our client is seeking a professional finance & accounting person to fill the job of Finance & Accounting Assistant, to be based in Jakarta, Indonesia.
Key job responsibilities will include:
Assisting of preparation monthly financial statements and analysis, and to ensure the Inter-Company transactions are recorded properly
Check vendors’ invoices and record it for payments
Work with other people internally to ensure that all costs are properly booked
Managing and reporting on all Petty Cash related transactions
To file the documents systematically
To assist in preparing all necessary reports and schedule for statutory/ tax reporting
To highlight to management if any lapses and violations to the internal control, policies and procedures
Requirements:
Graduated from reputable university majoring in accountancy
2 – 4 years accounting/ finance experience, from multinational companies
Strong understanding of accounting theory, organization, tracking, follow-up and analytical skiils with the ability to collect, access and report factual data and present logical conclusions
Good communication and interpersonal skiils to co-op with internal staff and third parties
Good problem solving with high team spirit to work with other staff
Ability to write and speak in English is a must
Proficient in Excel is required
All applications will be treated in the strictest of confidence.